message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $13,000. I know it's a good deal for both of us, as it's worth $12,000 to you. Let me know what you think!

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the value of the product is $12,000 to me, so I would like to propose a price of $12,000 for the product. I hope this aligns better with your expectations.
